Issue "cast mhash"

Or for the unfortunate sorcery deprived SAs
Please install mhash since sdelta uses mhash
to generate sha1 checksums.

export to the environment your desired CFLAGS and LDFLAGS.

For Linux and Solaris:
Then,    issue "make"
Finally, issue "make install" to have sdelta installed to /usr/bin

For FreeBSD:
Then,    issue "make bsd"
Finally, issue "make install"
